comp4432 game design studio game design studio provides you with an opportunity to practice and consolidate your game design skills the course builds on the iterative game design process taught in comp4431 game design workshop students work individually or in pairs to design prototype and playtest their own games while also expanding their understanding of the theory of game design by participating in a weekly reading group this course assumes familiarity with an appropriate game-development tool such as flash unity game maker or game salad 